features: 24-Month Hassle-Free Warranty, Easy to Reach Customer Service

Wired in ear headphones with built-in microphone and multifunctional button. Multifunctional button can pick up/end calls, play/pause music and rewind/fast-forward songs. Easily control phone calls and music with one button, ideal for exercising and sports activities.

Wired earbuds deliver a high-quality surround sound that is bass driven, delivering clarity for all kinds of music. Product also features a noise isolating earphone design, which significantly minimizes sound leakage and external noises, making it ideal for gaming, and commuting to school and work.

4 feet long tangle-free cord is made of premium TPE material that is strong, sturdy and durable. It is lightweight and portable with comfortable, ergonomic, interchangeable (small, medium, large) silicone earbud tips. Great for gaming, fitness, running, exercise, commuting, and in the airplane.
Compatible with iPhones, Androids, iPad, tablets, gaming controllers, iPods, Macbooks, computers; all devices with 3.5mm plug in audio jack. Some devices may require adapter (adapter not included)

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 23, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I bought two pairs! Since they were on a overstock sale and I am not disappointed at all! The sound is great and the fit is comfortable. Would recommend!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 7, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars I literally use these every day 5 days a week for over 5 months now.
reviews.reviewText: Worth every penny. I use these more than any other sound device for months on end now. 9 hours a day 5 days a week. Sound is clear, phone calls are clear. No issues.The rubber or plastic has yet to tear or show signs of wear. Cord is thick and flexible enough to handle daily use. Sound is great! mic is clear and picks up my voice well enough for phone calls.Great product and great value for the money.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 28, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars " Good sound, his and mids, light for runnig"
reviews.reviewText: "The sound quality is good, hi tones, and mids, but no lows. They do not seal properly because of their shape, particularly if you have wider ears, there for you won't hear bass notes. However, they are good for small ears.Great for listening to a speech, podcasts, or video tutorials. Also for running they're OK since they are very light, you won't even feel you have them on. The length of the cable is a bit short and tends to tangle because of the material. The control and mic work just as specified. Not the best but affordable. "
